          <p>Swapnil Biswas writes from Mumbai, where seven years in marketing and four in B2B SaaS have produced a particular kind of operator - one who is as comfortable in a fragment shader as in a positioning doc.</p>
          <p>A postgraduate in Digital Marketing and Growth Strategy from <em>IIM Visakhapatnam</em>, he treats his own career like a product: positioned, measured and shipped. The portfolio you are reading is itself a filing - designed, built and optimized by hand.</p>
